user_prompt: Suppose that a blimfet, a crongle, and a narzil are the leading bafwidgers. These are the only major bafwidgers, so if the crongle doesn’t bafwidge the most, then if the blimfet doesn’t bafwidge the most, the narzil will bafwidge the most. Does it follow that it’s likely that, if the blimfet doesn’t bafwidge the most, the narzil will?
